{"tid":2281664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤雄： 政府正研究是否需要資助學校的教師宣誓效忠基本法","createTime":"2020-11-11T10:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T14:38:40.000Z","uid":22556,"like":34,"dislike":164,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"cb50e2358afc5f0894f24539370488b621ca14d0","tid":2281664,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:15:12.000Z","msg":"今年 7 月 1 日或之後入職的政府公務員，必須按公務員事務局要求，宣誓擁護《基本法》、效忠香港特區並對特區政府負責。教育局局長楊潤雄今日（11 日）回覆民建聯議員張國鈞書面質詢，稱政府正研究上述宣誓安排，是否適用於資助學校的教師。有資深中學校長指，一般而言，資助學校教師的僱主是法團校董會，入職並非簽署公務員合約，並非拿取公務員薪酬待遇，如只在宣誓一項要求「睇齊」並不合理，「無理由責任一樣，權利不一樣。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3634922426593351/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3634922426593351%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEeSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=46114490\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3634922426593351/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"7940120398e42223bbff16bab6cc818f55403e96","tid":2281664,"uid":358571,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:17:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc23e65511c2ac877205ca74fa2621e28c1e2079","tid":2281664,"uid":20867,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"7940120398e42223bbff16bab6cc818f55403e96","tid":2281664,"uid":358571,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:17:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:20:29.000Z","msg":"半死不活 行屍走肉<br />\n<br />\n不如<br />\n<br />\n乾脆利落 一國一制"},{"pid":"e2e3d7896ab33c69d21fb227a1fe83eff975fdb9","tid":2281664,"uid":76804,"like":58,"dislike":3,"score":55,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:20:35.000Z","msg":"見到香港慢慢變到同中國其中一個市無分別<br />\n真係好心酸"},{"pid":"89e87ae117d86d2f5395c0869fb256648cde5b64","tid":2281664,"uid":50502,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:22:32.000Z","msg":"中國其他城市都唔洗宣誓咁撚肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas